message:
Hello Marcus Lee, I'm Fred Thompson, an SDR with Google. I noticed you were exploring Google Workspace (Enterprise Gmail). We have several options that could fit your business needs. Would you have 15–20 mins this week to chat?

Sincerely,
Fred Thompson
SDR | Google

Hi Fred Thompson—thanks for reaching out. Yes, we're interested. For context, I'm Marcus Lee, VP of Finance at FedEx. What Google Workspace (Enterprise Gmail) options do you recommend for a company in our industry? Also what does pricing generally look like?

Best,
Marcus Lee
VP of Finance | FedEx

Appreciate the details, Marcus Lee. For Google Workspace (Enterprise Gmail), common starting points include a pilot for one team and a security/compliance review. I can loop in an AE for a quick discovery to tailor SKUs and pricing (incl. annual vs. monthly). Does Tuesday 2:00–2:30 PM work for a discovery call?

Sincerely,
Fred Thompson
SDR | Google

Tuesday 2:00 PM works. Please send the calendar invite and any prep materials or a checklist for security review. If possible, include a quick comparison of tiers and a rough cost estimate.

Best,
Marcus Lee
VP of Finance | FedEx
